jmNA">Quảng Tế ký thắng - 廣濟記勝</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/author-ZRyB2U-4oqfhcjZ7xrf1_A">Nguyễn Du</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%A5c-Du/S%C6%A1n-th%C3%B4n-kinh-h%C3%A0nh-nh%C3%A2n-thi-d%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3c-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-FeMZ6ZIK_qUXttIXBy_YOA">Sơn thôn kinh hành nhân thi dược kỳ 1 - 山村經行因施藥其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%A5c-Du/author-6xOAUbKdWiBr-eAAn9zXQQ">Lục Du</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Nh%C3%A2n-T%C3%B4ng/S%C6%B0-%C4%91%E1%BB%87-v%E1%BA%A5n-%C4%91%C3%A1p/poem-SK_y8wVucpWN9zKU-mphNw">Sư đệ vấn đáp - 師弟問答</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Nh%C3%A2n-T%C3%B4ng/author-EY7jN0xHQfiiJpD91KwIgw">Trần Nhân Tông</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/S%E1%BB%AD-T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-V%C3%A2n-%C4%91%C3%ADch-thi-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-cH5_Qqx8c66lxYj0keJVhA">Sử Tương Vân đích thi kỳ 2 - 史湘雲的詩其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/author-1DK3jrzNRQ6A5gusK7iSPw">Tào Tuyết Cần</a>)<br></div>	</div>
